// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// CodeReview.ai — Prisma Schema (PostgreSQL + pgvector)
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

generator client {
  provider        = "prisma-client-js"
  previewFeatures = ["postgresqlExtensions"]
}

datasource db {
  provider   = "postgresql"
  extensions = [vector] // pgvector for code embeddings
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// ENUMS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

enum UserRole {
  USER
  ADMIN
}

enum MembershipRole {
  OWNER
  ADMIN
  MEMBER
}

enum PullRequestState {
  OPEN
  CLOSED
  MERGED
}

enum ReviewStatus {
  PENDING
  PROCESSING
  COMPLETED
  FAILED
}

enum CommentSeverity {
  ERROR
  WARNING
  INFO
  SUGGESTION
}

enum CommentCategory {
  SECURITY
  PERFORMANCE
  READABILITY
  MAINTAINABILITY
  BUG
  STYLE
}

enum ReviewPersona {
  CRITIC
  MENTOR
  OPTIMIZER
}

enum SubscriptionPlan {
  FREE
  PRO
  TEAM
  ENTERPRISE
}

enum SubscriptionStatus {
  ACTIVE
  CANCELED
  PAST_DUE
  TRIALING
}

enum NotificationType {
  REVIEW_COMPLETE
  PR_ANALYZED
  MENTION
  BILLING
  SYSTEM
}

enum ChatRole {
  USER
  ASSISTANT
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// MODELS
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

/// Platform user account, linked to Clerk for authentication.
model User {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  clerkId   String   @unique
  email     String   @unique
  name      String
  avatarUrl String?
  role      UserRole @default(USER)
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  repositories  Repository[]
  codeReviews   CodeReview[]    @relation("RequestedReviews")
  memberships   Membership[]
  notifications Notification[]
  chatSessions  ChatSession[]
  subscription  Subscription?
  usageLogs     UsageLog[]

  @@index([clerkId])
  @@index([email])
  @@map("users")
}

/// Organization (team) that can own repositories and have members.
model Organization {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  name      String
  slug      String   @unique
  avatarUrl String?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  memberships  Membership[]
  repositories Repository[]
  subscription Subscription?

  @@index([slug])
  @@map("organizations")
}

/// Join table linking Users to Organizations with a role.
model Membership {
  id             String         @id @default(cuid())
  userId         String
  organizationId String
  role           MembershipRole @default(MEMBER)
  createdAt      DateTime       @default(now())

  // Relations
  user         User         @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  organization Organization @relation(fields: [organizationId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, organizationId])
  @@index([userId])
  @@index([organizationId])
  @@map("memberships")
}

/// Connected GitHub repository.
model Repository {
  id             String    @id @default(cuid())
  githubId       Int       @unique
  name           String
  fullName       String
  description    String?
  private        Boolean   @default(false)
  defaultBranch  String    @default("main")
  language       String?
  stars          Int       @default(0)
  forks          Int       @default(0)
  webhookId      String?
  webhookSecret  String?
  isActive       Boolean   @default(true)
  lastAnalyzedAt DateTime?
  ownerId        String?
  organizationId String?
  createdAt      DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt      DateTime  @updatedAt

  // Relations
  owner        User?          @relation(fields: [ownerId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  organization Organization?  @relation(fields: [organizationId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  pullRequests PullRequest[]
  codeReviews  CodeReview[]
  chatSessions ChatSession[]
  embeddings   CodeEmbedding[]

  @@index([githubId])
  @@index([ownerId])
  @@index([organizationId])
  @@index([isActive])
  @@map("repositories")
}

/// GitHub Pull Request associated with a repository.
model PullRequest {
  id                String           @id @default(cuid())
  githubPrId        Int
  title             String
  body              String?          @db.Text
  state             PullRequestState @default(OPEN)
  headBranch        String
  baseBranch        String
  headSha           String
  baseSha           String
  additions         Int              @default(0)
  deletions         Int              @default(0)
  changedFiles      Int              @default(0)
  authorGithubLogin String
  githubUrl         String
  mergedAt          DateTime?
  repositoryId      String
  createdAt         DateTime         @default(now())
  updatedAt         DateTime         @updatedAt

  // Relations
  repository  Repository  @relation(fields: [repositoryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  codeReviews CodeReview[]
  commits     Commit[]

  @@unique([repositoryId, githubPrId])
  @@index([repositoryId])
  @@index([state])
  @@map("pull_requests")
}

/// Individual commit within a pull request.
model Commit {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  sha           String   @unique
  message       String   @db.Text
  authorName    String
  authorEmail   String
  committedAt   DateTime
  additions     Int      @default(0)
  deletions     Int      @default(0)
  pullRequestId String
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  pullRequest PullRequest @relation(fields: [pullRequestId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([pullRequestId])
  @@index([sha])
  @@map("commits")
}

/// AI-powered code review of a repository or pull request.
model CodeReview {
  id               String       @id @default(cuid())
  status           ReviewStatus @default(PENDING)
  overallScore     Float?
  readabilityScore Float?
  securityScore    Float?
  performanceScore Float?
  summary          String?      @db.Text
  repositoryId     String
  pullRequestId    String?
  requestedById    String
  modelUsed        String?
  tokensUsed       Int          @default(0)
  processingTimeMs Int?
  createdAt        DateTime     @default(now())
  updatedAt        DateTime     @updatedAt

  // Relations
  repository  Repository       @relation(fields: [repositoryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  pullRequest PullRequest?     @relation(fields: [pullRequestId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  requestedBy User             @relation("RequestedReviews", fields: [requestedById], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  comments    ReviewComment[]
  suggestions ReviewSuggestion[]

  @@index([repositoryId])
  @@index([pullRequestId])
  @@index([requestedById])
  @@index([status])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@map("code_reviews")
}

/// Individual comment on a code review, generated by the AI.
model ReviewComment {
  id           String          @id @default(cuid())
  codeReviewId String
  filePath     String
  lineStart    Int?
  lineEnd      Int?
  severity     CommentSeverity
  category     CommentCategory
  title        String
  body         String          @db.Text
  suggestion   String?         @db.Text
  persona      ReviewPersona
  isResolved   Boolean         @default(false)
  createdAt    DateTime        @default(now())

  // Relations
  codeReview CodeReview @relation(fields: [codeReviewId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([codeReviewId])
  @@index([severity])
  @@index([category])
  @@map("review_comments")
}

/// AI-suggested code fix within a code review.
model ReviewSuggestion {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  codeReviewId  String
  filePath      String
  originalCode  String   @db.Text
  suggestedCode String   @db.Text
  explanation   String   @db.Text
  isApplied     Boolean  @default(false)
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  codeReview CodeReview @relation(fields: [codeReviewId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([codeReviewId])
  @@map("review_suggestions")
}

/// Billing subscription for a user or organization.
model Subscription {
  id                   String             @id @default(cuid())
  userId               String?            @unique
  organizationId       String?            @unique
  stripeCustomerId     String?            @unique
  stripeSubscriptionId String?            @unique
  stripePriceId        String?
  plan                 SubscriptionPlan   @default(FREE)
  status               SubscriptionStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  currentPeriodStart   DateTime?
  currentPeriodEnd     DateTime?
  reviewsUsed          Int                @default(0)
  reviewsLimit         Int                @default(10)
  createdAt            DateTime           @default(now())
  updatedAt            DateTime           @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user         User?         @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  organization Organization? @relation(fields: [organizationId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([organizationId])
  @@index([stripeCustomerId])
  @@index([plan])
  @@map("subscriptions")
}

/// In-app notification sent to a user.
model Notification {
  id        String           @id @default(cuid())
  userId    String
  title     String
  body      String           @db.Text
  type      NotificationType
  isRead    Boolean          @default(false)
  metadata  Json?
  createdAt DateTime         @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([userId, isRead])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@map("notifications")
}

/// Conversational AI chat session scoped to a user and optionally a repo.
model ChatSession {
  id           String   @id @default(cuid())
  title        String?
  userId       String
  repositoryId String?
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user       User        @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  repository Repository? @relation(fields: [repositoryId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  messages   ChatMessage[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([repositoryId])
  @@map("chat_sessions")
}

/// Single message in a chat session.
model ChatMessage {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  chatSessionId String
  role          ChatRole
  content       String   @db.Text
  metadata      Json?
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  chatSession ChatSession @relation(fields: [chatSessionId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([chatSessionId])
  @@map("chat_messages")
}

/// Vector embedding of a code chunk for semantic search (pgvector).
model CodeEmbedding {
  id           String   @id @default(cuid())
  repositoryId String
  filePath     String
  chunkIndex   Int
  content      String   @db.Text
  // pgvector column — 1536 dimensions (OpenAI ada-002 compatible)
  embedding    Unsupported("vector(1536)")
  metadata     Json?
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  repository Repository @relation(fields: [repositoryId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([repositoryId, filePath, chunkIndex])
  @@index([repositoryId])
  @@map("code_embeddings")
}

/// Audit log for tracking AI usage (token consumption, model invocations).
model UsageLog {
  id         String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId     String
  action     String
  tokensUsed Int      @default(0)
  modelUsed  String?
  durationMs Int?
  metadata   Json?
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([action])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@map("usage_logs")
}
